    { question: "What can businesses and individuals do to navigate this economic uncertainty?", answer: "Businesses should focus on resilience, optimizing operations, and diversifying markets, while individuals can manage uncertainty by building financial reserves, diversifying investments, and staying informed about economic trends and policy changes." }
