    featuredImagePrompt: "A highly conceptual, thought-provoking image representing financial decisions and growth in the Indian IPO market. The central element is a stylized, glowing magnifying glass hovering over an abstract digital stock chart that shows an upward trend, with subtle Indian architectural elements or patterns integrated into the background. Blurred silhouettes of diverse investors (representing India, US, UK, Canada, Australia) are subtly visible, gazing towards the chart, symbolizing collective scrutiny and global interest. A sense of urgency and opportunity is conveyed through dynamic lighting and a vibrant, yet not overwhelming, color palette. Avoid any specific company logos or direct images of money, focusing on the abstract concept of investment analysis and market buzz.",
