    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing the convergence of AI chip design, startup investment, and market growth. The central element is an abstract, glowing network of interconnected AI chips and microprocessors, rendered with intricate digital pathways and light trails. Emanating from this network are upward-trending financial graphs and abstract data streams, symbolizing market rallies and rising valuations. Subtle, translucent outlines of global map continents (India, North America, Europe, Australia) are subtly integrated into the background, hinting at worldwide impact. The overall composition should convey innovation, acceleration, and interconnectedness in a vibrant, futuristic color palette of blues, greens, and gold, avoiding literal representations of companies or people.",
