    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing the seamless convergence of traditional finance and blockchain technology. On the left side, abstract symbols of traditional finance like subtle stock charts, a silhouette of a financial district skyline, and interlocked gears symbolizing market mechanisms are visible. On the right side, dynamic, glowing interconnected digital blocks, cryptocurrency symbols (like abstract representations of Bitcoin and Ethereum logos), and flowing data streams represent the blockchain world. A central, elegant bridge or a smooth, gradient transition connects these two distinct yet merging realms, symbolizing integration, innovation, and trust. The overall color palette should be professional and futuristic, incorporating deep blues, electric greens, and subtle gold accents. The image should convey sophistication, technological advancement, and the future of finance.",
