    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual, wide-angle visual representing the global interplay of cryptocurrency. On one side, abstract digital graphs and blockchain symbols intertwine with subtle American electoral elements (e.g., ballot boxes, flags in the background, not overtly political). In the center, a stylized, glowing \'MiCA\' text block with a European Union star circle subtly integrated, casting a light on a distressed but resilient Binance logo. On the other side, abstract financial data flows towards a stylized map outline of India, subtly hinting at its influence on local investors. The overall scene should convey interconnectedness, regulatory pressure, market volatility, and political influence, using a palette of deep blues, digital greens, and subtle gold accents. The focus is on the abstract forces, not specific people or highly detailed scenes. Avoid literal depictions of money or specific politicians.",
