      onChainMetrics: "On-chain metrics for Bitcoin (e.g., active addresses, transaction count, miner revenue, exchange flows) are closely watched indicators of network health and investor behavior, often reflecting underlying demand or selling pressure.",
      whaleActivity: "Whale activity (large holders) in Bitcoin is a significant market factor, with large transfers to or from exchanges often signaling potential buying or selling pressure, influencing short-term price movements.",
