      bearCase: "A more aggressive tightening cycle from the Federal Reserve, leading to sustained higher bond yields and increased cost of capital, could significantly depress valuations across risk assets, including AAVE. Regulatory crackdowns on DeFi or major security exploits could erode institutional trust and liquidity, causing a substantial price correction.",
