      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "We assign a 50% probability to a \'maturing but volatile\' outlook, 30% to \'increased regulatory headwinds,\' and 20% to \'continued speculative growth with pockets of innovation.\' The most likely scenario involves ongoing regulatory integration, leading to a more defined but potentially constrained operating environment for various crypto segments.",
      potentialCatalysts: ["Further regulatory clarity or enforcement actions against DeFi protocols.", "Major stablecoin issuers making further strategic product adjustments.", "High-profile successes or failures of AI-crypto convergence projects.", "Increased institutional adoption or rejection of prediction markets."],
