      neutralCase: "Anthropic\'s IPO is a landmark event for the AI industry, balancing immense growth potential with significant valuation and competitive risks. Its success will depend on its ability to translate technological leadership into sustainable revenue and profits. While the AI market\'s trajectory is undoubtedly upward, the specific performance of individual companies like Anthropic will be subject to market sentiment, execution, and evolving industry dynamics.",
