      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "We assign a moderately bullish probability-weighted outlook. While the bullish factors of market leadership, innovation, and AI integration are compelling, the significant valuation, execution risks, and competitive landscape necessitate a cautious approach. The probability of achieving all ambitious targets without significant setbacks is moderate, suggesting strong long-term potential but also considerable volatility in the short to medium term. The successful capital raise significantly de-risks immediate funding needs.",
