      bearCase: "A bear case scenario involves a recession-driven slowdown in freight and industrial demand, pressuring FedEx Freight and Dover. CarMax’s turnaround fails amid persistent margin compression, and high interest rates prolong retail headwinds. Regulatory or geopolitical shocks could exacerbate sector declines.",
