      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "Medium-term outlook: Neutral to mildly bullish. The positive momentum from infrastructure development and regulatory clarity around stablecoins is significant, but it will be tempered by ongoing market volatility, heightened regulatory scrutiny, and the need for publicly traded crypto firms to demonstrate clearer profitability paths. The risk of further enforcement actions against illicit activities remains a key concern.",
      potentialCatalysts: ["Accelerated adoption of regulated stablecoins for international trade and remittances.", "Successful integration of blockchain payment solutions by major financial institutions.", "Positive regulatory clarity from key jurisdictions on digital asset classification and market rules.", "Stronger-than-expected earnings reports from established crypto infrastructure providers.", "Increased institutional investment flows into digital asset funds and regulated crypto products."],
