      tokenOverview: "While the article covers various crypto aspects, stablecoins are central to Trace Finance\'s operations. Stablecoins are cryptocurrencies designed to minimize price volatility, typically pegged to a fiat currency like the US Dollar. They serve as a crucial bridge between traditional finance and the crypto world, facilitating efficient cross-border transactions and acting as a store of value within the digital asset ecosystem.",
      tokenUtility: "For Trace Finance, stablecoins provide the core utility for near-instant, low-cost cross-border settlements, bypassing traditional banking intermediaries. This utility is particularly valuable for businesses engaged in international trade, offering greater efficiency and transparency compared to conventional SWIFT transfers. BitGo\'s infrastructure supports various tokens, providing custody and security services essential for institutional participation.",
