      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "The probability-weighted outlook suggests a cautious optimism. There\'s a high probability of continued innovation and integration of AI in finance (70%), but also a significant probability of increased regulatory scrutiny (80%) and market volatility (75%). The likelihood of highly speculative or fraudulent projects persisting is moderate (60%), with a lower probability of widespread, immediate mainstream adoption of novel crypto-AI consumer products until underlying technologies mature and regulatory clarity improves (40%). The overall impact on market structure will be high, driven by automation and new risk profiles.",
