    executiveSummary: "The Indian IPO market is gearing up for a high-profile listing with Kalyan Jewellers\' upcoming IPO. The company aims to raise Rs 1,750 crore through the IPO, which is set to open on June 10 and close on June 12. With a price band of Rs 86-87 per share, Kalyan Jewellers\' valuation is expected to be around Rs 12,000 crore post-IPO.",
